---
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="How We Work" id="how-we-work">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Strategic guidance. <span class="text-primary">Collaborative expertise</span>.
    Focused planning for long-term clarity and confidence.
  </Fragment>

  <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-default bg-default p-6">
      <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-primary">
        Comprehensive Planning
      </h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-offset">
        We don’t sell products. We build coordinated financial strategies that
        align investments, insurance, tax planning, and estate considerations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-lg border border-default bg-default p-6">
      <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-primary">
        Collaborative Approach
      </h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-offset">
        We work alongside your CPA, attorney, and other advisors to ensure
        nothing is duplicated, missed, or working against your goals.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-lg border border-default bg-default p-6">
      <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-primary">
        Long-Term Focus
      </h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-offset">
        Our planning is designed to adapt as your life and business evolve —
        helping you protect what you’ve built and grow your legacy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
